  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hello and welcome to Dodot! I designed Dodot as a simple, fun pre-game. In Dodot, you click on balls to collect points, and the more you click, the higher you climb on the leaderboard. It's a delightful way to warm up before diving into an FPS game. With its smooth, user-friendly interface, you can easily regain your focus and continue your fun exactly where you left off.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All you need to do is click!</p>",
